<doc id="1235071" wikidata="Q115677" url="?curid=1235071" title="Max de Terra">
<text>Max de Terra (6 October 1918 – 29 December 1982) was a Swiss racing driver. He participated in two Formula One World Championship Grands Prix, debuting on 18 May 1952. He scored no championship points.

He was a member of the Ecurie Espadon.

