<doc id="1235290" wikidata="Q7766027" url="?curid=1235290" title="The Sporting News Manager of the Year Award">
<text>The &quot;The Sporting News&quot; Manager of the Year Award was established in 1936 by &quot;The Sporting News&quot; (formerly &quot;Sporting News&quot; from 2002 to 2022) and was given annually to one manager in Major League Baseball. In 1986 it was expanded to honor one manager from each league.

